Zomato Customer Retention Analysis


Objective:
Use Python to predict customer churn and
suggest offers to retain them.

Dataset:

Use Zomato or food delivery dataset (CustomerID,OrderFrequency, LastOrder, Rating, Complaints).
Steps:
Use Pandas to clean & transform
Feature engineering: Avg Order Gap, Order
Rating
Build Logistic Regression model to predict
churn

Recommend actions for high-risk users
